Kers are real pissed"},{"pid":"1e6698da703df883cf414ac32f5a9f62d7812d39","tid":1544461,"uid":97944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:42:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1ff11d8b1ce2421e56aaa26117b14e8f78baf553","tid":1544461,"uid":270374,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:43:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">而家最急嘅唔係五大訴求<br />\n好大機死咗人啊！全部推831！係不停推！因為會秒沉<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1544276/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1544276/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n到底失蹤傷者去咗邊？？？？<br />\n點解我哋無人去港鐵總部大樓要求交CCTV ？</span>"},{"pid":"88665343bb5d9cc8a3d6b3503da56ab269af912e","tid":1544461,"uid":277644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:43:18.000Z","msg":"u know me bro<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ece337efbe173bd86a4824e96bbea700db60417","tid":1544461,"uid":166634,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:43:25.000Z","msg":"LINK:<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/CECCgov/status/1169619233308925953\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCECCgov%2Fstatus%2F1169619233308925953&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWMIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=d98ae5d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCECCgov%2Fstatus%2F1169619233308925953&h=1bf84470\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/CECCgov/status/1169619233308925953</a>"},{"pid":"9e082b398a29ef3131c1c1fd62aa80a5d1822c42","tid":1544461,"uid":72800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:43:50.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><blockquote><em>我們成長為自由人。 沒人可讓一個自由的人下跪。<br />\nWe grew up as free people. <br />\nNo one can make a free person kneel.</em><br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\"><strong><del>WINTER ON FIRE</del><br />\n《HONG KONG BE WATER》</strong></span></blockquote></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">港共企圖以<strong>錄音、撤回、學季開始</strong><br />\n轉移<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">太子地鐵站傷亡</span>、<br />\n六警壓脊椎休克 <span style=\"color: teal;\">至今嚴重昏迷</span>、<br />\n新屋嶺事件、<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">阻止民主人權法案</span></strong></span>、<br />\n模糊 臥底實彈、武警滲透、<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">清朝債主權問題</span></span>等<br />\n</strong>連串<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>核彈</strong></span>事件焦點<br />\n</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">林鄭錄音：事件現時已經上升至「國家主權及國家安全的層次，\n加上世界兩大經濟體前所未有的張力」，她可以做的已經非常少。</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><blockquote><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英、美、德 領事館請願 大遊行</span></span></strong><br />\n國際審視中英聯合聲明 法定性<br />\n中共正統性<br />\n中共毀約 無視國際社會<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />請求國際介入香港前途</span></span></strong> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">施壓制裁港府 <br />\n還原港人高度自治 落實港人雙普選 <br />\n協助<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重新制定</span></span>民主進程<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n香港人道災難 <strong>高壓滅聲</strong> 白色恐怖 <br />\n執法機器無法無天 受命中共 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">港府管治班子自治權名存實亡</span>  聽命中央</span><br />\n實彈恐嚇 威嚇扼殺<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">民主自由</span>現代普世價值<br />\n<br />\n重申 <strong><ins>五大政諫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />全面落實</ins></strong><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: green;\">驅逐共黨 光復香港<br />\n華夏遺珠 高度自治</span> </em></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">人權民主法案</span> 事在必行</strong></blockquote></div><br />\n<br />\n破而後立<br />\n國際自由港🕊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">這不單是 反修例活動<br />\n這是屬於香港人的<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時代革命</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>流水革命 元年</div></ins></span></strong>"},{"pid":"a1ea3d10c2dadf2e694b5f065c824c37c9ba6e51","tid":1544461,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:44:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8bf57c9dfce5562987301474f69a897604e951f","tid":1544461,"uid":835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:45:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0555f2257035d6a3605fdb7495a6c496504c107","tid":1544461,"uid":116914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:45:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f718d3eb65ca8c153c65d6dbdd9da069bdc8a2f","tid":1544461,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:45:55.000Z","msg":"推<br />\nsir this way"},{"pid":"1dc43e64e66b140757ddfff8f84c57abbd8a08b7","tid":1544461,"uid":74642,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:46:13.000Z","msg":"幫手share出去<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">airdrop！印出黎！派街坊<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/05/224232_d660935b085d1a2a5f9c220a7068c69e.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F05%2F224232_d660935b085d1a2a5f9c220a7068c69e.jpeg&h=34fe012b&s={SIZE}\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n&lt;願榮光歸香港&gt;請大家一齊文宣！印歌詞派！等更多人識唱<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/154446